{"word":"κομιδή","slug":"κομιδή","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n58788\" key=\"komidh/\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">κομῐδή</orth>, <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">ἡ</gen>, (<etym lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"etym\">κομίζω</etym>) <sense id=\"n58788.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">attendance, care</tr_>, <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Hom.</author></bibl>, etc.; in <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author></bibl>, of <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">care bestowed on horses</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:8:186\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">8.186</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:23:411\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">23.411</biblScope> </bibl>; in <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author></bibl>, of <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">care bestowed on men</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:8:453\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">8.453</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:14:124\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">14.124</biblScope> </bibl>; also, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">care bestowed on</tr_> a garden, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">οὐ πρασιή τοι ἄνευ κομιδῆς κατὰ κῆπον</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:24:247\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">24.247</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseu